The most powerful open source node-based application for creating images, videos, and audio with GenAI.
=======================================================================================================

Credit: [Paul Trillo](https://www.instagram.com/paultrillo/), [makeitrad](https://x.com/makeitrad1), Lenovo, [Rui](https://x.com/rui40000) using [Animatediff](https://github.com/Kosinkadink/ComfyUI-AnimateDiff-Evolved) & [Controlnets](https://github.com/Kosinkadink/ComfyUI-Advanced-ControlNet), [Hakoniwa](https://x.com/8co28), [Andidea](https://www.andidea.jp/) team using [CogVideoX](https://github.com/kijai/ComfyUI-CogVideoXWrapper), [Joanna L](https://www.instagram.com/jyolyyyu/), [Vrch Studio](https://www.vrch.io/) using [ComfyUI Web Viewer](https://github.com/VrchStudio/comfyui-web-viewer) & [Live Portrait](https://github.com/PowerHouseMan/ComfyUI-AdvancedLivePortrait)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Our features

Your creativity, unlocked with AI
=================================

Videos & Images

3D & Realtime

Audio

Videos & Images
===============

Generate videos & images using the latest open source models.
-------------------------------------------------------------

[View Examples](https://www.comfy.org/videos)

Video credits: [Paul Trillo](https://www.instagram.com/paultrillo/), [makeitrad](https://x.com/makeitrad1), and others. Made for Lenovo.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Customize your workflow
=======================

with custom nodes
=================

Many of the most popular capabilities in ComfyUI are written as custom nodes by the community: Animatediff, IPAdapter, CogVideoX and more.

[Learn more](https://docs.comfy.org/essentials/custom_node_overview)
